499
00:23:57.965 --> 00:24:00.255
Community Schools are public schools that partner

500
00:24:00.255 --> 00:24:02.295
with stakeholders to create the conditions

501
00:24:02.575 --> 00:24:03.775
students need to thrive.

502
00:24:04.805 --> 00:24:07.735
Community schools can be found across the United States,

503
00:24:08.235 --> 00:24:09.935
and their numbers are growing fast.

504
00:24:11.515 --> 00:24:14.615
But what exactly makes a school a community school?

505
00:24:15.485 --> 00:24:19.215
They integrate student supports, clinics, counselors,

506
00:24:19.275 --> 00:24:20.895
and other services ensure each

507
00:24:20.955 --> 00:24:22.935
